WEBVTT

00:00:01.548 --> 00:00:05.286
So, let me thank you
for the opportunity to talk about

00:00:05.310 --> 00:00:10.378
the biggest international story
of your professional lifetime,

00:00:10.402 --> 00:00:14.303
which is also the most important
international challenge

00:00:14.327 --> 00:00:17.490
the world will face
for as far as the eye can see.

00:00:17.514 --> 00:00:19.653
The story, of course,
is the rise of China.

00:00:20.106 --> 00:00:23.915
Never before have so many people
risen so far so fast,

00:00:23.939 --> 00:00:25.750
on so many different dimensions.

00:00:26.336 --> 00:00:30.086
The challenge is the impact
of China's rise --